results.name: Decimal expansion of the integer Googol!.
comment: The last nonzero term of this sequence is 6. [From _Washington Bomfim_, Dec 24 2010]
reference: Ronald L. Graham, Donald E. Knuth and Oren Patashnik, Concrete Math.; section 4, exercises 40, and 54.
